        What Happens If the Buyer Defaults at Settlement in Queensland 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A buyer who cannot settle is a stressful situation, but Queensland law gives vendors meaningful protections and options. Here is what you need to know.
      </p>
